DETAILS

Memory Map

   0-64  Able main

     0-1    boot
     1-2    tasks
     2-     code
    32-64   recv buff

  64-128  reserved for deployment

 128-192  Able Forth

   128-129  task
   129-130  eval buff
   130-132  send buff
   132-     code

 192-256  reserved for bootstrap

 256-     free

1024 byte blocks
